title: Relaxation - Sounds of the Earth: Waterfall
description:
Sounds of the Earth:

Waterfall
--------------------

A small waterfall is running, with a variety of sounds, splashes,
trickles, and drips. Hear the water gushing down, cleansing and
purifying everything in its constant flow

Total Time: 66:00

---

Sounds of the Earth offers pure nature sounds, no voices are
added, no music is added, no human-induced noises are heard.
Sounds of the Earth bids you welcome to the wild and the
fragile sounds of nature.

---

Enjoy!
